{"tid":1447232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"個夢好恐怖 驚到札醒","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:49.000Z","uid":97200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"43c8dda6a4a9ccee173d44d73b01af68bef9697c","tid":1447232,"uid":97200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"見到手足被不人道對待<br />\n射爆絲打隻眼 地鐵站放tg 警犬著黑衫扮示威者<br />\n煽動真示威者暴力衝擊 北角放生襲擊記者嘅暴徒<br />\n黑警亳無底線 香港無法可依<br />\n頂唔順走去瞓左陣<br />\n<br />\n夢見有人捉左警嫂同警犬仔女<br />\n之後仲邊笑邊凌遲佢地 <br />\n又要佢地笑住咁食返自己嘅肉<br />\n見到咁嚇到札醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發埋啲咁嘅夢好不安<br />\n有冇巴絲教我點做<br />\n係咪壓力太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da6dbf4676ee11c574800099a64551fe9170547","tid":1447232,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:13.000Z","msg":"1. 少女被射眼已致盲<br />\n2. 721白衣無一起訴<br />\n3. 狗扮示威者掟磚放火<br />\n4. 室內射tear gas波及市民<br />\n5. 過期tear gas毫無回應<br />\n6. 武警混入黑警破壞一國兩制<br />\n <img src=\"https://puu.sh/E3Wfd/7d2ecd4e3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpuu.sh%2FE3Wfd%2F7d2ecd4e3c.jpg&h=1a4c7a03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://puu.sh/E3Wfn/237acf8969.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpuu.sh%2FE3Wfn%2F237acf8969.jpg&h=47044ca5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A2JizBQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA2JizBQ.jpg&h=9763c09f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"2f4c491cb3198b32786e11c3b2b7266b3b47fc28","tid":1447232,"uid":34063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:14.000Z","msg":"邊個話我哋輸緊嘅我屌晒你哋老母！要嬴嘅全部同我入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dBbvRS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dBbvRS</a><